{"tid":459974,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用戶發現iPhone X陰陽屏：畫面痛苦","createTime":"2017-11-06T08:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T12:30:10.000Z","uid":141060,"like":39,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d670ef99136ed73601e3aafd08ac26d0748ef73c","tid":459974,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"上周末，蘋果主動公布了一則預警，表示iPhone X雖然采用了蘋果認為滿足其嚴苛標准的一塊優秀的OLED屏幕，但是依然逃脫不了一些OLED的通病，比如燒屏、P排的子像素共占對分辨率的侵占。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/165251_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F165251_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=a1fd6bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燒屏一般需要OLED一定時間的使用才會出現，短則三五月，長則幾年。不過陰陽屏、亮度不均等基本素質問題已經開始浮現。<br />\n據SoftPedia收集整理，Reddit上用戶爆料的iPhone X屏幕BUG是，亮度最低在暗光下，上部明亮，下部過暗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/165336_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F165336_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=008f963c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這名用戶表示自己懷疑屏幕是質量問題，他已經聯系蘋果官方解決，對方尚未給出明確回應。<br />\n一般，蘋果不會公布屏幕供應商，但大家普遍認為，iPhone X的這塊異形切割全面屏來自三星，後者代表著業界OLED的最高水准。<br />\n此前，谷歌Pixel 2 XL也因為LG的P-OLED側面發藍、陰陽屏、燒屏、黑斑等問題遭受爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/165402_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F165402_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=476a1628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/165405_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F165405_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=1ad9bad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/165408_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F165408_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=d69c7df4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"907ec096bad404d91a16c22527e31d23e91963fb","tid":459974,"uid":8014,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"用家問題"},{"pid":"cd04f457dfc378606dd0ec178b5c08b9880bd0ed","tid":459974,"uid":9232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"年經"},{"pid":"6a65915e99a507972c1c159fba72fbd49d72c98d","tid":459974,"uid":135986,"like":153,"dislike":10,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"之前idog又話買an機做烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家成皮嘢買塊烙印mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ni狗呢 出嚟吠返兩聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4a283d919f9e44a649845948b76f87ae79a0a0","tid":459974,"uid":9232,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"不過apple唔同，多人圍屌下佢會認數"},{"pid":"80e54c24b8d3d57d1a5c0659972a027ad5b6148f","tid":459974,"uid":45189,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"係咁架喇 <br />\n又無人迫你買<br />\n係咪先"},{"pid":"96592a07c55fc2c03f4b94b1903d7245a221beeb","tid":459974,"uid":138131,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"等集體出紫線"},{"pid":"30fd7274faaad59489c127c076d47ab50d5cc020","tid":459974,"uid":38173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb221dac4dd938740c1c40b44bfc13d0f04947a","tid":459974,"uid":56634,"like":39,"dislike":5,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"乜撚野質量問題<br />\n太重壓壞左個mon?<i